<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PaLTM2.9.8">
<l>kēcava ṉēyiṅkē pōta rāyē</l>
<l rend="indent">killēṉeṉ ṉātiṅkē pōta rāyē</l>
<l>nēcami lātā rakatti runtu</l>
<l rend="indent">nīviḷai yāṭātē pōta rāyē</l>
<l>tūcaṉam collum toḻuttai mārum</l>
<l rend="indent">toṇṭarum niṉṟa viṭattil niṉṟu</l>
<l>tāycolluk koḷvatu taṉmam kaṇṭāy</l>
<l rend="indent">tāmōta rāviṅkē pōta rāyē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Keśava! Come here!</l>
<l rend="indent">Come here without saying “I can’t!”</l>
<l>Don’t you play in the houses of unloving people!</l>
<l>Stay away from the places where slave women</l>
<l rend="indent">and servants say terrible things,</l>
<l>Considering the words of [your] mother</l>
<l rend="indent">is your dharma, Dāmōdara! Come here!</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
